# Changelog

## [0.3.30]
### Fixed
- replace all rxjs operators first() with take(1)

## [0.3.29]
### Fixed
- (DynamicTableDataSource): refresh issue

## [0.3.28]
### Fixed
- (DataSourceDirective): dynamic subscriptions

## [0.3.27]
### Fixed
- (BaseHttpDataSource): encode the url path params

## [0.3.26]
### Added
- DynamicTableDataSource

## [0.3.25]
### Fixed
- (DataSourceCollection): run outside zone issue

## [0.3.24]
### Fixed
- (DataSourceCollection): change detection after the data source emits data

## [0.3.23]
### Added
- (BaseDataSource): add the change$ property to notify when the data source changes.

## [0.3.22]
### Fixed
- change detection issue

## [0.3.21]
### Changed
- optional paginator

## [0.3.20]
### Changed
- (BaseHttpDataSource) cache request options

## [0.3.19]
### Added
- BaseHttpDataSource

## [0.3.18]
### Changed
- Allow async tableEventToHttpOptions

## [0.3.17]
### Fixed
- fix requests in progress counter decrease.

## [0.3.16]
### Added
- ng-update support

## [0.3.15]
### Fixed
- (TableDataSource): add the startWith operators to SortChange Observable

## [0.3.14]
### Added
- License

## [0.3.13]
### Fixed
- add missing Injectable decorator to StaticDataSource

## [0.3.12]
### Changed
- use the angular OnDestroy concept to cleanup data sources

## [0.3.11]
### Fixed
- default TableDataSource metadata

## [0.3.10]
### Changed
- Change the viewer id to an optional property

## [0.3.9]
### Added
- ToTableDataSourcePipe

## [0.3.8]
### Changed
- allow operations change before the PipeDataSource is initialised

## [0.3.7]
### Changed
- operations are only execute once per source data source change in PipeDataSource
### Fix
- init() call in the BaseDataSource._connect method

## [0.3.6]
### Changed
- update peer dependencies

## [0.3.5]
### Added
- RXAP_HTTP_TABLE_DATA_SOURCE_TO_OPTIONS_FUNCTION
- RXAP_HTTP_PAGINATION_DATA_SOURCE_TO_OPTIONS_FUNCTION
- TableEventToHttpOptions function
- PageEventToHttpOptions function
- Custom *DataSource decorators
### Removed
- To context and routes concept
### Changed
- add the *ToHttpOptions

## [0.3.4]
### Changed
- add withCredentials and responseType support to HttpDataSource

## [0.3.3]
### Added
- AbstractTableDataSource
- RxapHttpDataSourceError
- RxapHttpTableDataSourceError
- RxapTableDataSourceError
- HttpTableDataSource
- TableDataSourceDirective
- ToHttpTableDataSource
- RXAP_TABLE_DATA_SOURCE_PAGINATOR
- RXAP_TABLE_DATA_SOURCE_SORT
- RXAP_TABLE_DATA_SOURCE_FILTER
- RXAP_TABLE_DATA_SOURCE
### Changed
- Move the PageEvent and PaginatorLike interfaces to @rxap/data-source/pagination
- Add utility methods to AbstractPaginationDataSource
- Rewrite TableDataSource

## [0.3.2]
### Added
- PaginationDataSourceDirective
- HttpPaginationDataSource
- ToPaginationPipe
- ToHttpPaginationPipe
- AbstractPaginationDataSource
- IdOrInstanceOrInjectable
### Changed
- Split the PaginationDataSource into AbstractPaginationDataSource and PaginationDataSource
- Call the connect method in *DataSourceDirective separately
- Call the connect method in *DataSourceDirective in the AfterViewInit Hook


## [0.3.1]
### Fixed
- remove dependency to @rxap/services

## [0.3.0]
## Added
- RXAP_DATA_SOURCE_METADATA InjectionToken

## [0.2.3]
### Added
- rxapDataSourceCollection directive

## [0.2.2]
### Added
- Changelog file
- Add new interceptor system
- @rxap/data-source/http
- Add PipeDataSource
- Add ObservableDataSource
### Removed
- @rxap/data-source/recorder
### Deprecated
- @rxap/data-source/open-api
- HttpDataSource in @rxap/data-source
